Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:16.88,top,SORA,0,0,0,,When cats are happy,\Nthey show it in various ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:21.06,main,SORA,0,0,0,,Like purring, or raising their tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:22.42,main,YUKI,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:24.58,main,SORA,0,0,0,,Mugishima is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:26.22,italics,YUKI,0,0,0,,Huh? Mugishima?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:30.78,main,SORA,0,0,0,,What happens when she's happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:36.40,main,YUKI,0,0,0,,Ohh, so you want\Nto make Mugishima happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:37.40,main,SORA,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:39.33,main,YUKI,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:41.21,main,YUKI,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:45.70,main,YUKI,0,0,0,,If you do something\Nthat makes you happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:47.47,main,YUKI,0,0,0,,maybe she'll be happy too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:49.48,main,SORA,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:54.62,main,KINAKO,0,0,0,,When it comes down to it,\Nyou should just strike a weird pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:59.60,main,KINAKO,0,0,0,,Humans are happy\Njust seeing cats in weird poses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:03.55,main,SORA,0,0,0,,{\t(2100,2400,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Hmm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:06.41,main,SORA,0,0,0,,Mugishima?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:07.39,main,MUGISHIMA,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:11.10,italics,SORA,0,0,0,,Something that makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:14.32,italics,SORA,0,0,0,,The throat-petting thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:22.94,main,MUGISHIMA,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:28.38,main,MUGISHIMA,0,0,0,,Ah, Sora, could you put this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.54,0:01:30.24,main,SORA,0,0,0,,Hm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:33.22,main,SORA,0,0,0,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:36.51,main,MUGISHIMA,0,0,0,,It's a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:39.23,main,MUGISHIMA,0,0,0,,Because it's been getting cold lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:42.60,main,SORA,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:46.04,main,SORA,0,0,0,,It matches yours, Mugishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:48.44,italics,MUGISHIMA,0,0,0,,Yeah, it looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:52.57,italics,SORA,0,0,0,,Oh my, Mugishima looks happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:57.64,flashback,KINAKO,0,0,0,,Humans get happy over weird poses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:00.31,italics,SORA,0,0,0,,I'll strike a funny pose, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:04.23,main,SORA,0,0,0,,Mhmm, mhmm, just like that.
